            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken skewers</strong> to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) and pull up the edges of the foil to form an open parcel (this will collect any juices!)</p><p>Pour the <strong>remaining marinade</strong> all over and put the tray[s] under the grill for 16-18 min, turning once halfway, until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>honey sesame free range chicken skewers</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
