        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While everything is cooking, combine your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>with your <strong>toasted sesame oil </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this your <strong>pickled sesame dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
