            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cooked rice</strong> topped with the <strong>honey sesame free range chicken skewers</strong> and the <strong>cucumber</strong> <strong>batons</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Whisk your <strong>mayo </strong>into<strong> </strong>any <strong>juices</strong> left from the chicken and drizzle it all over the chicken and rice, then top the shredded lettuce with the <strong>pickled sesame dressing </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Serve the mayo to the side plain and leave the dressing!</span></strong></p>",
